<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>Hatak pi̱ kana puta ma ƲIT80</title>
<time_sig>(8.7.8.7.)</time_sig>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Hatak pi̱ kana puta ma!
 Chibbak e halʋlli kʋt,
 E chi aiokpahanchi hosh,
 E chi̱ hullo fehnʋshke.

[V2]
 Himak nitak fehna hoka
 Ish pibafoka chi̱ ka
 Ʋlhpiesa, aiahni hosh,
 E chi holitoblishke.

[V3]
 Pi̱ kana hʋchia hokʋt,
 Ʋba aiachukmaka
 Ish piakaiya pulla na,
 Pi a yukpa pullʋshke.

[V4]
 Nitak moma himak pilla
 Il iti halʋllashke;
 Achukmali pulla hocha,
 Il iti̱ hoyullashke.

[V5]
 Chisʋs pi̱ Shahli chia ma,
 Okla e moma hoka
 Ish pi aiokpahanchashke;
 Ahnit e chim ilbʋsha.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>80</hymn_number>
<author>Cyrus Byington</author>
</song>